Package: BasicMC
Type: Package
Title: Formation of transition matrix from raw data, simple analysis and applications of finite-state discrete time-homogeneous Markov Chain 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ziqing Ho
Maintainer: Ziqing Ho <zh2n15@soton.ac.uk>
Description: Form a transition matrix from raw data. Classify recurrent, transient and absorbing states, calculate the n-step transition probabilities and conditional distribution, carry out simple simulation and applications of finite-state discrete time-homogeneous Markov Chain. 
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: igraph, methods 
Encoding: UTF-8
License: GPL (>=2)
LazyData: true
